---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Readings with Vanessa | Tarot Flower"
  description="Personal tarot readings with Vanessa for clarity, reflection, and guidance."
  image="/images/readings-with-vanessa/vanessa-shuffling-teal-tarot-cards.png"
>
  <main class="readings-with-vanessa">
    <header class="readings-hero container">
      <h1>Readings with Vanessa</h1>
      <p>Personal tarot readings for clarity, reflection, and guidance.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="readings-sections container">
      <section class="readings-section">
        <div class="readings-image readings-image--portrait">
          <img
            src="/images/readings-with-vanessa/vanessa-shuffling-teal-tarot-cards.png"
            alt="Vanessa smiling while shuffling teal tarot cards"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="readings-copy">
          <h2>A Reading with Vanessa</h2>
          <p>A tarot reading is a space to pause, look more deeply, and listen to what is asking for your attention.</p>
          <p>You may arrive with a specific question, a decision you are navigating, or simply the feeling that something in your life is shifting.</p>
          <p>Together, we'll explore the cards, the patterns unfolding around you, and the possibilities available to you now.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="readings-section">
        <div class="readings-copy">
          <h2>How I Read</h2>
          <p>I don't use tarot to tell you what your future must be.</p>
          <p>I use the cards as a language of symbols, intuition, reflection, and possibility.</p>
          <p>A reading with me is an open conversation. I'll share what I see, ask questions, and help you connect the messages in the cards to your own life, instincts, and experience.</p>
          <p>The purpose is not to give your authority away. It is to help you hear yourself more clearly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="readings-image readings-image--portrait">
          <img
            src="/images/readings-with-vanessa/vanessa-holding-empress-card.png"
            alt="Vanessa smiling while holding the Empress tarot card"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="readings-section">
        <div class="readings-image readings-image--landscape">
          <img
            src="/images/readings-with-vanessa/tarot-cards-candlelight-smoke.png"
            alt="Hands shuffling tarot cards beside candlelight, crystals, and rising smoke"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="readings-copy readings-booking">
          <h2>Book a Reading</h2>
          <p>Bring a question, a crossroads, a relationship, a creative idea, or anything else you would like to explore.</p>
          <p>You don't need to know anything about tarot, and you don't need to arrive with the perfect question. We'll begin wherever you are.</p>
          <p class="readings-format">60-minute online reading</p>
          <p class="readings-price">$100 USD</p>
          <a class="readings-button" href="/checkout/readings-with-vanessa/">Book a Reading</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
